=== RDF Provider ===

==== Functionality ====
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.DisplayConfigurationWidget
| clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.provider.RDFProvider
| type = 'DESCRIPTION'
}}
Go back to [[Help:Providers | Providers ]]

==== Configuration Settings ====
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.DisplayConfigurationWidget
| clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.provider.RDFProvider
}}

The RDF format of the source can be optionally specified and selected from the offered supported formats. If not specified explicitly, the ''RDFProvider'' inspects the HTTP content-type of the response or alternatively the extension of the file in the URL.

==== Example ====

Consider as an example that you want to import an RDF dump of the ''Mondial'' metadata.

This can be achieved by configuring an ''RDFProvider'' on [[Admin:Providers]] with the source ''<nowiki>http://www.dbis.informatik.uni-goettingen.de/Mondial/Mondial-RDF/mondial-europe.rdf</nowiki>''
